        Deprecated.
        Does a given operation on two numbers.
        Parameters:
        num1 - the first number of the operation.
        num2 - the second number of the operation.
        op - the operation to be performed.
        update - whether to update the current state.
        Returns:
        the result of the operation.
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - iff num1 or num2 are null. Note that either num1 OR num2 will be this.
